== Concern Group of Hong Kong Entrepreneur Policy ==
Kelvin was the Chairman of Drafting Committee of "Concern Group of Hong Kong Entrepreneur Policy". This concern group has established in 2015 and it aims to assist youth entrepreneur in starting up their business. A press conference was held in The City University of Hong Kong successfully on 24 January 2016. This press conference was being covered by over 10 media like Yahoo! News,<ref>{{cite news|title=調查顯示青年對本港創業政策不太滿意|url=https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/video/調查顯示青年對本港創業政策不太滿意-112103109.html|accessdate=5 February 2016|publisher=現代電視|date=24 January 2016}}</ref> Hong Kong Economic Journal,<ref>{{cite news|title=午睡屋涉違例 90後創業怨乏支援|url=http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/1228951/午睡屋涉違例+90後創業怨乏支援|accessdate=5 February 2016|agency=紀曉風|work=Hong Kong Economic Journal|date=25 January 2016}}</ref> Hong Kong Economic Times,<ref>{{cite news|title=青年不滿政府創業政策　批缺乏支援|url=http://topick.hket.com/article/1204902/青年不滿政府創業政策%E3%80%80批缺乏支援|accessdate=5 February 2016|work=Hong Kong Economic Times|date=24 January 2016}}</ref> StartUpBeat,<ref>{{cite web|last1=Wan|first1=Phoenix|title=香港青年創業政策可以走得更前|url=http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=25759|work=Hong Kong Economic Journal|accessdate=5 February 2016}}</ref> HK01,<ref>{{cite news|title=你見過未？　95%創業者未曾申請政府基金|url=http://www.hk01.com/即日新聞/4105/你見過未-95-創業者未曾申請政府基金|accessdate=5 February 2016|agency=方心惠|issue=25 January 2016|publisher=HK01}}</ref> Sky Post,<ref>{{cite news|title=9成半年輕創業者 無申資助|url=http://www.skypost.hk/港聞/新聞/20160125/001/9成半年輕創業者%20無申資助/204453|accessdate=5 February 2016|work=Sky Post|date=25 January 2016}}</ref> Sun Daily,<ref>{{cite news|title=手續繁複 95%創業者未申基金|url=http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20160125/00407_027.html|accessdate=5 February 2016|work=Sun Daily|date=25 January 2016}}</ref> Oriental Daily News<ref>{{cite news|title=手續繁金額少　95%青年創業家無申政府基金|url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160124/mobile/bkn-20160124180939224-0124_00822_001.html|accessdate=5 February 2016|publisher=Oriental Daily News|date=24 January 2016}}</r